251Nahetupaccayā naārammaṇapaccayā naadhipatipaccayā naanantarapaccayā nasamanantarapaccayā naaññamaññapaccayā naupanissayapaccayā napurejātapaccayā napacchājātapaccayā naāsevanapaccayā nakammapaccayā navipākapaccayā naāhārapaccayā naindriyapaccayā najhānapaccayā namaggapaccayā nasampayuttapaccayā navippayuttapaccayā nonatthipaccayā novigate ekaṃ.
252Nahetumūlakaṃ.
